data.description: Elegant 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home for sale in the heart of Fayetteville. This beautiful home includes a recently converted garage that added 400 heated and cooled sq feet to the original 1550 sq feet. This addition can be used as a game room, second living room, or fourth bedroom. Currently being used as an Airbnb. Passed all city inspections. Other amenities include storm shelter and private porch off the master bedroom.
